#Text=( ( WN ( Joseph Ford ) ) ) Does Molossia have its own flag , currency or national anthem ?
#Text=President Baugh : Absolutely , what would a country be without those things ?
#Text=Our flag has three horizontal stripes , blue , white and green ( from the top ) .

#Text=The blue stands for the Molossian sky , almost always blue , the white stands for the nearby mountains , white with snow much of the year , and the green stands for the green of the desert foliage in the spring .
#Text=It flies every day in front of Government House .
#Text=Our currency is the Valora , and comes in both paper and coin formats , the latter being poker chips , instead of traditional coins .
#Text=Our national anthem is " Molossia , Nation in the Desert " , with lyrics written by me and set to the Albanian national anthem .

column1: #Text=I 'm sure they do n't mind .
#Text=( ( WN ( Joseph Ford ) ) ) What is the official language of Molossia ?
#Text=President Baugh : Our official language is English , but we borrow from Esperanto sometimes , such as for the name of our capital , " Espera " and our money the Valora .
#Text=We have no problem borrowing from other languages , as well , and we also use the Deseret Alphabet as an alternate writing script .
#Text=( ( WN ( Joseph Ford ) ) ) What is the governmental structure of Molossia ?
#Text=President Baugh : Well , officially , Molossia is a republic , complete with a constitution .
#Text=Sadly , things are in such disarray over the border from us , that I had no choice but to suspend the constitution and declare martial law .
#Text=It 's unfortunate , but the security of my nation is paramount , and the best way to ensure that is to rule by decree .
#Text=So far , no one has complained , and anyway , I 'm a rather benevolent dictator .
#Text=( ( WN ( Joseph Ford ) ) ) Does Molossia have its own military ?
#Text=President Baugh : Yes , we do , the mighty Molossian Navy .
#Text=Yes , we have a Navy in the desert .
#Text=Our Navy has been involved in several exploration expeditions during its three years of existence .
#Text=We are quite proud of our Navy .
#Text=( ( WN ( Joseph Ford ) ) )
#Text=The Molossian Navy has their own academy , which is open for all to join online .
#Text=Tell us about that .

#Text=President Baugh : Indeed , I opened the Naval Academy several years ago as the Molossian Military Academy , taking advantage of my strong military background . When I founded the Molossian Navy , it was natural to turn the Military Academy into and Naval Academy .
#Text=In the years before and since , the Academy has produced dozens of graduates .
#Text=The Academy is free to all applicants , and includes lessons and tests on military leadership , tactics , seamanship and naval battles .
#Text=Once an individual has taken all four tests successfully , he or she can purchase a certificate of completion , and can then purchase on honorary commission in the Molossian Navy .
#Text=We offer honorary commissions in the rank of captain , commodore and admiral .
